			<CASNumber>10043-35-3</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Anhydrous boric acid in powder form, a material characterized by the absence of water content (anhydrous), presented as a fine powder. This product has undergone specific processing to achieve anhydrous state and powdered form. It conforms to applicable quality and industry standards for chemical products. The description indicates its form and purity, which are important for users in various applications such as industrial manufacturing and laboratory use. The production route is typically from the reaction of boron compounds with acids. This substance is provided for use as part of production processes, as well as to end consumers, depending on the intended use specified in the product's documentation.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">无水硼酸粉末，是一种没有水分内容（无水）的材料，以细粉末形态呈现。该产品经过特定加工处理达到无水状态和粉末形态。它符合化学产品的适用质量和行业标准。说明中指出了其形态和纯度，对于工业制造和实验室使用等多种应用的用户来说非常重要。其生产路线通常是由硼化合物与酸反应制得。该物质根据产品文件中指定的预定用途，提供给生产流程使用，以及最终消费者。</common:generalComment>
